title: Shares fall on worries over GDP growth (Shanghai Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Shanghai Municipal Government ) Shanghai 's share index yesterday fell from an eight-week high amid investor concern over China's slowest quarterly economic growth since 2009. The Shanghai Composite Index shed 0.14 percent to 3,386.7
